Package jain.protocol.ip.sip.message

Interface Summary
Message This interface represents a generic SIP Message.
MessageFactory This interface provides factory methods to allow an application create Messages from a particular JAIN SIP implementation.
Request This interface represents a SIP Request i.e. a request from a client to a server.
Response This interface represents a SIP Response message.
